# ✅ Extra Protection (Recommended)

### ✅ SameSite

```js
sameSite: "lax"
```

Stops most cross‑site cookie attacks automatically

### ✅ Use POST (never GET)

```http
POST /refresh
```

### ✅ HTTPS

```js
secure: true
```

